{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1015,"text":"This story starts with these two --"},{"time":4032,"text":"my kids."},{"time":5314,"text":"We were hiking in the Oakland woods"},{"time":7020,"text":"when my daughter noticed\na plastic tub of cat litter in a creek."},{"time":11647,"text":"She looked at me and said,"},{"time":13333,"text":"\"Daddy?"},{"time":15864,"text":"That doesn't go there.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":17538,"text":"When she said that,\nit reminded me of summer camp."},{"time":19984,"text":"On the morning of visiting day,"},{"time":21506,"text":"right before they'd let our anxious\nparents come barreling through the gates,"},{"time":25193,"text":"our camp director would say,"},{"time":26586,"text":"\"Quick! Everyone pick up\nfive pieces of litter.\""},{"time":28919,"text":"You get a couple hundred kids\neach picking up five pieces,"},{"time":31983,"text":"and pretty soon, you've got\na much cleaner camp."},{"time":34580,"text":"So I thought,"},{"time":35763,"text":"why not apply that crowdsourced\ncleanup model to the entire planet?"},{"time":40324,"text":"And that was the inspiration\nfor Litterati."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43299,"text":"The vision is to create\na litter-free world."},{"time":46672,"text":"Let me show you how it started."},{"time":48204,"text":"I took a picture of a cigarette\nusing Instagram."},{"time":52222,"text":"Then I took another photo ..."},{"time":54113,"text":"and another photo ..."},{"time":55694,"text":"and another photo."},{"time":56885,"text":"And I noticed two things:"},{"time":58195,"text":"one, litter became artistic\nand approachable;"},{"time":62244,"text":"and two,"},{"time":63419,"text":"at the end of a few days,\nI had 50 photos on my phone"},{"time":65958,"text":"and I had picked up each piece,"},{"time":67569,"text":"and I realized that I was keeping a record"},{"time":69978,"text":"of the positive impact\nI was having on the planet."},{"time":73153,"text":"That's 50 less things that you might see,"},{"time":75365,"text":"or you might step on,"},{"time":76632,"text":"or some bird might eat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78769,"text":"So I started telling people\nwhat I was doing,"},{"time":81445,"text":"and they started participating."},{"time":84831,"text":"One day,"},{"time":86548,"text":"this photo showed up from China."},{"time":90039,"text":"And that's when I realized"},{"time":91334,"text":"that Litterati was more\nthan just pretty pictures;"},{"time":94624,"text":"we were becoming a community\nthat was collecting data."},{"time":98869,"text":"Each photo tells a story."},{"time":101279,"text":"It tells us who picked up what,"},{"time":103496,"text":"a geotag tells us where"},{"time":105531,"text":"and a time stamp tells us when."},{"time":108006,"text":"So I built a Google map,"},{"time":110459,"text":"and started plotting the points\nwhere pieces were being picked up."},{"time":114536,"text":"And through that process,\nthe community grew"},{"time":118478,"text":"and the data grew."},{"time":120806,"text":"My two kids go to school\nright in that bullseye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125125,"text":"Litter:"},{"time":126360,"text":"it's blending into\nthe background of our lives."},{"time":129088,"text":"But what if we brought it\nto the forefront?"},{"time":131211,"text":"What if we understood exactly\nwhat was on our streets,"},{"time":134147,"text":"our sidewalks"},{"time":135560,"text":"and our school yards?"},{"time":137122,"text":"How might we use that data\nto make a difference?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":141189,"text":"Well, let me show you."},{"time":142411,"text":"The first is with cities."},{"time":144418,"text":"San Francisco wanted to understand\nwhat percentage of litter was cigarettes."},{"time":149081,"text":"Why?"},{"time":150267,"text":"To create a tax."},{"time":152073,"text":"So they put a couple of people\nin the streets"},{"time":154232,"text":"with pencils and clipboards,"},{"time":155617,"text":"who walked around collecting information"},{"time":157704,"text":"which led to a 20-cent tax\non all cigarette sales."},{"time":161787,"text":"And then they got sued"},{"time":163964,"text":"by big tobacco,"},{"time":165164,"text":"who claimed that collecting information\nwith pencils and clipboards"},{"time":168404,"text":"is neither precise nor provable."},{"time":171454,"text":"The city called me and asked\nif our technology could help."},{"time":175158,"text":"I'm not sure they realized"},{"time":176431,"text":"that our technology\nwas my Instagram account --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178703,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179766,"text":"But I said, \"Yes, we can.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":181056,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":182096,"text":"\"And we can tell you\nif that's a Parliament or a Pall Mall."},{"time":186028,"text":"Plus, every photograph\nis geotagged and time-stamped,"},{"time":189477,"text":"providing you with proof.\""},{"time":191839,"text":"Four days and 5,000 pieces later,"},{"time":195083,"text":"our data was used in court\nto not only defend but double the tax,"},{"time":200045,"text":"generating an annual recurring revenue\nof four million dollars"},{"time":204392,"text":"for San Francisco to clean itself up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208001,"text":"Now, during that process\nI learned two things:"},{"time":210260,"text":"one, Instagram is not the right tool --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":212838,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":213893,"text":"so we built an app."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215420,"text":"And two, if you think about it,"},{"time":217077,"text":"every city in the world\nhas a unique litter fingerprint,"},{"time":220718,"text":"and that fingerprint provides\nboth the source of the problem"},{"time":224578,"text":"and the path to the solution."},{"time":227646,"text":"If you could generate a revenue stream"},{"time":230048,"text":"just by understanding\nthe percentage of cigarettes,"},{"time":232535,"text":"well, what about coffee cups"},{"time":234655,"text":"or soda cans"},{"time":236385,"text":"or plastic bottles?"},{"time":238501,"text":"If you could fingerprint San Francisco,\nwell, how about Oakland"},{"time":241726,"text":"or Amsterdam"},{"time":243446,"text":"or somewhere much closer to home?"},{"time":247408,"text":"And what about brands?"},{"time":248666,"text":"How might they use this data"},{"time":250591,"text":"to align their environmental\nand economic interests?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":255646,"text":"There's a block in downtown Oakland\nthat's covered in blight."},{"time":259325,"text":"The Litterati community got together\nand picked up 1,500 pieces."},{"time":263812,"text":"And here's what we learned:"},{"time":265176,"text":"most of that litter came\nfrom a very well-known taco brand."},{"time":269738,"text":"Most of that brand's litter\nwere their own hot sauce packets,"},{"time":274438,"text":"and most of those hot sauce packets\nhadn't even been opened."},{"time":279965,"text":"The problem and the path\nto the solution --"},{"time":282704,"text":"well, maybe that brand only\ngives out hot sauce upon request"},{"time":286689,"text":"or installs bulk dispensers"},{"time":288722,"text":"or comes up with more\nsustainable packaging."},{"time":291298,"text":"How does a brand take\nan environmental hazard,"},{"time":294291,"text":"turn it into an economic engine"},{"time":296321,"text":"and become an industry hero?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":299292,"text":"If you really want to create change,"},{"time":301518,"text":"there's no better place to start\nthan with our kids."},{"time":304416,"text":"A group of fifth graders picked up\n1,247 pieces of litter"},{"time":307843,"text":"just on their school yard."},{"time":309715,"text":"And they learned that the most\ncommon type of litter"},{"time":312271,"text":"were the plastic straw wrappers\nfrom their own cafeteria."},{"time":315947,"text":"So these kids went\nto their principal and asked,"},{"time":318500,"text":"\"Why are we still buying straws?\""},{"time":321166,"text":"And they stopped."},{"time":322945,"text":"And they learned that individually\nthey could each make a difference,"},{"time":326623,"text":"but together they created an impact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329503,"text":"It doesn't matter\nif you're a student or a scientist,"},{"time":333539,"text":"whether you live in Honolulu or Hanoi,"},{"time":336698,"text":"this is a community for everyone."},{"time":339974,"text":"It started because of two little kids\nin the Northern California woods,"},{"time":344677,"text":"and today it's spread across the world."},{"time":347938,"text":"And you know how we're getting there?"},{"time":350067,"text":"One piece at a time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352508,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353747,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}